# ── Signing key (NEVER commit) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# The derived public key + extension ID live in extension-key.json (committed).
# The private key only lives locally / in the WXT_CHROME_KEY Actions secret.
key.pem
*.pem
!extension-key.json
